to do a little bit custom.

22:18.745 --> 22:20.829
- Yeah.
- So--but even then,

22:20.914 --> 22:22.498
while it's getting painted,

22:22.582 --> 22:23.924
I can do the interior
and get everything else done.

22:24.009 --> 22:26.510
- Leon and Lynn,
the owners of this car,

22:26.669 --> 22:28.420
thought that
the dash was spray-painted,

